    public final class RotOrder

    This class is a utility representing a rotation order specification for Cardan or Euler angles specification. This class cannot be instantiated by the user. He can only use one of the twelve predefined supported orders as an argument to either the Rot.Rot(RotOrder,float,float,float) constructor or the Rot.getAngles(shapes3d.utils.RotOrder) method.
